These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, strawberry, lime
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, pilot, architect
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, adventure, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, brazilian
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, scooter, roller
 1. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
 2. the fan of soul is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 3. the person eating lime is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the brazilian##1
 5. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 7. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 9. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
10. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the fan of funk##8
11. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
12. the fan of pop is not to the right of the pilot##8
13. the fan of pop is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person eating potato##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato | strawberry | lime    |
| Job           | teacher | pilot   | architect     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts     | adventure   | thriller       |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | pop   | soul     |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | malaysian   | russian |
| Transport     | roller     | tram | scooter     |

