.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, cooking
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, lawyer, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, r&b, ambient
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, russian, german
3 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, ferret
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, tennis
 1. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 2. the russian is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of r&b##1
 4. the police-officer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 5. the german is on the left or right of the designer##3
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the designer##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
 9. the russian is not the fan of electronic##6
10. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the russian is not to the right of the pakistani##8
12. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
13. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the lawyer and the owner of the ferret##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | cooking | collecting | magic-tricks |
| Job           | lawyer     | designer     | police-officer     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic       | r&b      | ambient     |
| Nationality   | german     | russian   | pakistani  |
| Pet           | goat        | lizard       | ferret   |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | rugby    | tennis     |

