 6. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 7. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
10. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the nurse##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
13. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
14. the nurse is the brazilian##1

