 1. the fan of salsa is not the person eating pomegranate##6
 2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the pakistani is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the fan of trance##6
 6. the person drinking juice is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
 7. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
 8. the owner of the frog is the pakistani##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is not the fan of trance##6
10. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5
11. the person eating pomegranate is not the fan of metal##6
12. the turkish is on the left of the australian##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
