 3. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
 4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##5
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person driving the motorbike##8
 8. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
10. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person eating orange and the fan of hip-hop##7

.:: Answer ::.
