 9. the architect is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
10. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching documentary movies and the person driving the scooter##2
11. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the manager##1
12. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | almond-milk         | tea      |
| Hobby         | puzzles     | video-games         | card-games    |
| Job           | architect  | designer | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary    | horror        | spy      |
| Sport         | biathlon  | parkour        | cycling    |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi      | scooter      |

